{"tid":2493341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【屌你老母無人講？】CNN自認利用市民對武肺恐懼，控制民心，推高收視，制造輿論，做瘟疫政治打手，竟然無人講？？？","createTime":"2021-04-17T22:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T04:34:06.000Z","uid":88743,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e154eb32a4de2cc695fa77fc2b018bddfcd2e79","tid":2493341,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9faQkIA6YNU&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fd867729\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9faQkIA6YNU</a><br />\n<br />\n專登係右邊大字寫死亡人數<br />\n每日都要提你呢啲數字<br />\n驚你唔記得左「疫情係好撚恐佈」呢回事<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhRnAdPkgLhnKCu5ut6EjoSuRpkC95XHvxXCTqjXEvZP?filename=6wjaVoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wjaVoM.jpg&h=175a63d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVYykjJy7pWYER53Lw2aEW2QsqiuTw17wW6fQjkNMXcdG?filename=XwQmhB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwQmhB6.jpg&h=cb03e30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死亡數字越高越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUhpDicf6xjmLwctBgLh5QxaAKADCxYEaJj8VEz5rFuoZ?filename=SDu2Mvr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDu2Mvr.jpg&h=b9870538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數字越高，我地帶出既論點【防疫措施】就越多人BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeUcTwkdvVrpgGYLxmad9AtU8NeryCbC11NiDeW1N95JQ?filename=G75YjQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG75YjQr.jpg&h=c920f74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恐懼可以帶起收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbAPy2HpPn7Sp2UFkBRePYsTHYNYYJsfq21836FWnT3Fc?filename=Z24qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ24qKg6.jpg&h=f2de3732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐懼會KEEP住令你日日睇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3jQfUm9a86NSqPsJbDHS4cUK1EVJvRh8qX1ypnWYN6D?filename=CZ9qKg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZ9qKg6.jpg&h=f065fcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n流得越多血，收視越高／防疫論點越多人BUY<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXfcupx3uJDfzEo6s6GBWxi5DdHLksdbjsWT9MwdYXrHV?filename=UOvYjQs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOvYjQs.jpg&h=255cc5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無人將我上面既野講出口，不過其實係好明顯既心理現像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQAYvJQAaYyDemibMppTVffZiKhQJAxWXGrTHHWGvx8Hq?filename=aPS4foM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPS4foM.jpg&h=730bb0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIf it bleeds, it leads<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n越死得人多，收視越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死得人多，就可以make our point better (我地講既野越有說服力)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">最重要講左佢地點解唔報康復人數<br />\n因為康復人數唔會令到你地驚</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZdP5MnzbpjYx4GRzHmSpKqE7xHRy47Ksm4dwJKqxMVTY?filename=j5y7daM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5y7daM.jpg&h=883cbc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcs3jx8gW1b2HVaaBVC6ko6HaEr8B28ykokodzte1Q5V4?filename=wbQYjQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbQYjQM.jpg&h=01ea213a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP3EirM3pbKDJFkYU5mXaYX8RV1HqoSXjXGEAMNzDuiym?filename=WxOGhDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxOGhDu.jpg&h=eff5d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報完之後人地成個Twitter account又俾人BAN鳩埋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma78vZTk7TQmhmDPncK99RxJanDUucxc5w3vSbdYqVLAG?filename=20pRETa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20pRETa.jpg&h=578b4044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n侵侵個仔都有retweet呢單野<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme8fDj5Yk7Xpa9vjbCNvwg6xVZxuxe1n4B7eyPUgHt3HP?filename=mLd3v23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLd3v23.jpg&h=23a05085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇返香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfJotXdozGf4ja5edFP2PqotmZUofiS1H16vvKt3gtcaM?filename=9qPRERW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qPRERW.jpg&h=5021cb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmm7mxPyhUc4TPKDRpo98pTdGv4YwEk8dS6fZ4VQRcsW?filename=uorkybV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuorkybV.jpg&h=42f595bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVxTpDgiMKTTYggbtzFRxYg7MbZ2GkWSHm9a5m1qDaYBh?filename=2Ks4fqf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Ks4fqf.jpg&h=a3807bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmakf8PxkTc61tKKPLNKizEEAxXcqvmHJY6DhgubxdKWfv?filename=p5sWQYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5sWQYT.png&h=83002d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">香港啲傳媒同自媒體有邊個有報呢單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"67bd1588e234ecae55a131bbdf55a3d91f664ddb","tid":2493341,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:32:41.000Z","msg":"三日前架啦喎屌"},{"pid":"c01cf10c7ce479fac066b3a1f83d9ce1a15176c0","tid":2493341,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:34:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得劍橋分析？"},{"pid":"8c5459d1134c3221d9645686ece1caf2aa644bcd","tid":2493341,"uid":245201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:35:49.000Z","msg":"國屍走得太前"},{"pid":"64f7026d03719d66b546d73229d74b8303cbe460","tid":2493341,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c01cf10c7ce479fac066b3a1f83d9ce1a15176c0","tid":2493341,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:34:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得劍橋分析？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:36:27.000Z","msg":"咩劍橋分析<br />\n<br />\n我淨係知呢啲PO係連登出左一定勁撚多人入黎拉PO"},{"pid":"4f2d40c696a3ce47f2b74fefec6a0217bc0be96b","tid":2493341,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T22:38:05.000Z","msg":"依家佢地擺明畀世人知道佢地做緊嘅野，吹咩？<br />\n<br />\n即使有日佢地自爆話武肺其實係作出黎，世人又可以奈佢地咩何？"},